The Best of Belinda, Volume 1 is the fifth album by American singer Belinda Carlisle, released in 1992 (see 1992 in music) by Virgin Records. It is a best of compilation album, a collection of Carlisle's hits from 1986 to 1991. It is the only Carlisle album to have topped the UK Albums Chart.


